{"type":"message","id":"82cbbff7","parentId":"d01fc240","timestamp":"2026-05-12T10:35:54.775Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Jo wants to know how to call the local qwen2.5:7b model. Let me explain the ways to use it with ollama.\n","thinkingSignature":"48eb087ae4d7ed5f216c9ec41fc8f67d74c99068f5b85a093d200785272a0f76"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**呼叫本機 qwen2.5:7b 的幾種方式：**\n\n---\n\n## 1. 直接用 ollama CLI\n```bash\nollama run qwen2.5:7b\n```\n然後直接打字問它，輸入 `/bye` 結束。\n\n---\n\n## 2. Python 呼叫（建議）\n```python\nimport ollama\n\nresponse = ollama.chat(\n    model='qwen2.5:7b',\n    messages=[\n        {'role': 'user', 'content': '你的問題'}\n    ]\n)\nprint(response['message']['content'])\n```\n\n---\n\n## 3. 在 Ray 腳本裡呼叫\n你現有的 `ray_brain.py` 或 `ray_cloud_brain.py` 應該有用 ollama，直接說「用 qwen2.5:7b 分析 XXX」我就可以幫你跑。\n\n---\n\n## 4. 終端機單次問答\n```bash\nollama generate qwen2.5:7b \"解釋一下什麼是 Sharpe Ratio\"\n```\n\n---\n\n**Qwen2.5:7b vs Qwen2.5:1.5b 比較：**\n\n| | 7B | 1.5B |\n|--|--|--|\n| 速度 | 較慢 | 較快 |\n| 智慧 | 較強 | 夠用 |\n| VRAM 需求 | ~6GB | ~2GB |\n\n你的 ray-deep-v1（7B）和 qwen2.5:7b 差不多，都是大模型。要我示範叫用嗎？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":7594,"output":365,"cacheRead":31616,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39575,"cost":{"input":0.0022781999999999998,"output":0.00043799999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0018969599999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00461316}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778582135559,"responseId":"0652357ee99623a2240ab0fc156b333b"}}
