219.4 | 68.5 🟡 | 175.9 | +0.73 | 0.90   | 16.2% | 動能放緩       |\\n| AMAT | 443.6 | 66.5    | 161.3 | +3.17 | 2.96   | 19.0% | 健康多頭       |\\n| LRCX | 296.1 | 66.5    | 142.9 | +2.87 | 2.47   | 21.6% | 健康多頭       |\\n\\n科技巨頭 — 分化\\n\\n| 股票    | 價格    | RSI     | KDJ   | MACD  | 評價        |\\n| ----- | ----- | ------- | ----- | ----- | --------- |\\n| QQQ   | 713.3 | 83.2 🔴 | 105.3 | +3.95 | 接近超買      |\\n| AAPL  | 292.7 | 72.4    | 129.0 | +2.0  | 偏多        |\\n| GOOGL | 388.6 | 71.6    | 47.3  | +2.98 | 偏多        |\\n| AMZN  | 269.0 | 68.8    | 20.9  | -0.41 | 🟡 MACD轉負 |\\n| META  | 598.9 | 39.2    | -28.1 | -7.18 | 🟢 空方訊號   |\\n\\n資安 / 雲端 — 補漲輪動\\n\\n| 股票   | 價格    | RSI  | MACD  | 評價    |\\n| ---- | ----- | ---- | ----- | ----- |\\n| PANW |…[truncated]\"\n}\n```","display":false,"details":{"source":"openclaw-runtime-context"},"id":"82a6ea17","parentId":"c93c27f1","timestamp":"2026-05-12T11:10:01.278Z"}
{"type":"message","id":"6eb354b0","parentId":"82a6ea17","timestamp":"2026-05-12T11:10:45.713Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Jo is asking me to critique the rule \"TWII RSI > 85 時不加倉美股\" (don't add positions in US stocks when TWII RSI > 85) and propose improvements. Let me analyze this rule critically.\n\nThe context from the report shows:\n- TWII RSI was estimated at ~93, way above 85\n- But the analysis also showed QCOM/MU/INTC/AMD all had RSI > 80\n- The rule blocked adding US positions based on Taiwan market overbought\n\nLet me think about what's good and what's problematic about this rule:\n\n**What's good about the rule:**\n1. Acknowledges cross-market correlation (TW -> US through TSM supply chain)\n\n\n2. TWII RSI > 85 means Taiwan is overbought, and when it's had a big run, a correction could drag down US tech stocks tied to TSM\n3. Acts as a circuit breaker to prevent chasing positions at high risk\n\n**What's problematic:**\n1. TWII and US tech don't always move in lockstep—sometimes US markets rally while Taiwan corrects\n2. The 85 threshold is arbitrary and doesn't account for sector specifics; an ETF like VEA or VOO might be fine even when TWII is overbought\n3. The rule's logic is backwards—it assumes Taiwan's overbought condition means US stocks are automatically risky, but correlation isn't that simple\n4. Looking at the actual case, TWII RSI ~93 reflects theindex itself being overbought, not necessarily indicating anything about US stock valuations or correlations\n5. The current rule doesn't distinguish between different types of US exposure—TSM-heavy semiconductor plays versus broad market ETFs like VOO/VTI have different risk profiles\n6. There's a blind spot around sector-specific correlations—NVDA and AMD might actually be driven more by global AI trends than by Taiwan's market movements\n7. The VIX reading of 19.0 seems more immediately relevant for US trading decisions than the TWII RSI threshold\n\nI should propose a more nuanced framework that accounts for these distinctions.\n","thinkingSignature":"bc24392c9b04ff6098d64ee0c76d76eeb142dd0ed5247d84574ca6eac14bb4f6"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n## 檢討：TWII RSI > 85 不加倉美股\n\n### ⚠️ 原始規定問題\n\n| 問題 | 說明 |\n|------|------|\n| **邏輯跳躍** | TWII RSI 是台灣加權指數的技術指標，跟美股半導體/ETF 沒有直接因果關係 |\n| **門檻過於主觀** | 85 這個數字沒有量化根據 |\n| **單一指標** | 只看 RSI，忽略 VIX、原油、韓股等更重要指標 |\n| **不分行類** | VOO/QQQ/VEA/個別科技股風險完全不同，一刀切 |\n| **今天實例** | TWII RSI ~93 但 QCOM/MU/INTC 的問題是「自己 RSI 過高」，不是台股影響 |\n\n---\n\n### ✅ 改善方案：多因子聯鎖條件\n\n```\n加倉美股時，同時滿足以下 ALL：\n1. TWII RSI < 80（放寬到 80，且是必要非充分）\n2. VIX < 25（市場情緒穩定，美股系統性風險低）\n3. WTI 原油 < 95（排除通膨失控情境）\n4. 目標標的 RSI < 75（個股自己不能太貴）\n5. 美股趨勢向上（MA20 > MA60）\n\n滿足以下任一條件，禁加倉：\n✗ VIX > 25（市場恐慌）\n✗ TWII RSI > 90（台股明顯過熱）\n✗ 原物料快速上漲（通膨風險）\n✗ 標的 RSI > 80（自己已經超買）\n```\n\n---\n\n### 📋 門檻建議\n\n| 指標 | 禁區（Red Zone） | 警戒區（Yellow） | 安全區（Green） |\n|------|-----------------|-----------------|----------------|\n| TWII RSI | > 90 | 80-90 | < 80 |\n| VIX | > 25 | 20-25 | < 20 |\n| 原油 | > 100 | 90-100 | < 90 |\n| 個股 RSI | > 80 | 70-80 | < 70 |\n\n---\n\n### 💡 核心邏輯修正\n\n舊邏輯：`台股過熱 → 不買美股`（過度簡化）\n\n新邏輯：\n- **台股過熱** → 注意 TSM ADR 連動风险，但不直接禁美股\n- **VIX 高** → 才是系統性風險，美股全面觀望\n- **原油大漲** → Fed 降息預期降溫，科技股估值壓力\n- **個股 RSI 80+** → 才是技術面進場紀律問題\n\n**TWII RSI > 85 應該只是黃燈預警，不是紅燈直接禁。** 改成「注意 TSM 連動」而非「不買美股」，精準多了。\n\n要我更新 AGENTS.md 寫入這套新規則嗎？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2895,"output":1076,"cacheRead":40256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44227,"cost":{"input":0.0008684999999999999,"output":0.0012912,"cacheRead":0.0024153599999999996,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004575059999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778584201278,"responseId":"06523d8bd4cba1e8a8113e996725e1ea"}}
