{"type":"message","id":"f45531f3","parentId":"9419880a","timestamp":"2026-05-12T11:28:44.796Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The qwen3.5:4b model is returning empty responses consistently. This is likely because the model's thinking output is captured separately, and the actual text response is stripped. Looking at the Ollama API docs, for models with thinking enabled, the response content might be in a different field.\n\nLet me check what fields the response actually contains by printing the full JSON with all keys.\n\nActually let me think about this differently. The issue might be that the model generates a very long thinking block, and the actual response content is short. When we set num_predict to a small value, the model might be hitting the thinking token budget first, leaving nothing for the actual response.\n \nI'm wondering if the thinking parameter is disabled on our qwen3.5:4b but still enabled by default on ray-v3, which would explain why we see empty content there. Maybe I should test with a more direct question like \"1+1等於幾?\" to bypass the thinking chains entirely.\n","thinkingSignature":"2cfcefa633b823c34e52f80aa44d21bffd3d3af388c43ff2ec97167427ad05f7"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_1e9kf7hd35dt_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"import urllib.request, json\n\nurl = \"http://localhost:11434/api/chat\"\nmessages = [{\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": \"1+1等於幾？直接回答數字\"}]\ndata = {\n    \"model\": \"qwen3.5:4b\",\n    \"messages\": messages,\n    \"stream\": False,\n    \"options\": {\n        \"temperature\": 0.5,\n        \"num_predict\": 20\n    }\n}\n\nbody = json.dumps(data).encode(\"utf-8\")\nreq = urllib.request.Request(url, data=body, headers={\"Content-Type\": \"application/json\"})\n\nwith urllib.request.urlopen(req, timeout=30) as resp:\n    raw = resp.read().decode(\"utf-8\")\n    result = json.loads(raw)\n\nprint(\"Keys:\", list(result.keys()))\nmsg = result.get(\"message\", {})\nprint(\"Message keys:\", list(msg.keys()))\nprint(\"Content:\", repr(msg.get(\"content\", \"\")))\nprint(\"Done:\", result.get(\"done\", False))","path":"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray\\test_minimal.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":151,"output":462,"cacheRead":81152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81765,"cost":{"input":0.000045299999999999997,"output":0.0005543999999999999,"cacheRead":0.004869119999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005468819999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778585312153,"responseId":"065241e2a0fedb3b9967fac7d53455f1"}}
