{"type":"message","id":"01044669","parentId":"379832a2","timestamp":"2026-05-12T11:29:47.236Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The Ollama server seems to be hanging when processing requests. The qwen3.5:4b model with its thinking mode is taking very long to respond. The first few times we got empty responses, which means the thinking mode was triggered but the response was empty (maybe it failed to produce output or the thinking consumed everything).\n\nLet me try something simpler - let me check if the Ollama server is responsive at all using the ps command. Also, let me check what version of Ollama is running.\n\nActually, let me try using the `ollama ps` command to see if the server is even alive.\n","thinkingSignature":"6adc9ef32968cf8b3262f8a0e55b47e42b96bcb75c877c1c8083a98b6a5e60f2"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4m6d7id88ghx_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ollama ps 2>&1","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":280,"output":166,"cacheRead":82432,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82878,"cost":{"input":0.000084,"output":0.0001992,"cacheRead":0.0049459199999999995,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005229119999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778585379326,"responseId":"06524224e6abb124af16b50357ac5d2f"}}
