{"type":"message","id":"ac72d1d4","parentId":"c41d8083","timestamp":"2026-05-12T11:29:56.916Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Ollama is running but no model is currently loaded (no process showing). The issue is that qwen3.5:4b loads slowly (8 seconds load time) and the API call needs the model loaded first. Also the model might be swapping due to memory constraints.\n\nThe key issue: qwen3.5:4b is a 3.4GB model and your system has 16GB RAM. With Windows taking ~8-10GB, there's maybe 6-8GB available. Ollama would need to load the model weights into RAM, and when answering, it also needs VRAM if there's a GPU. Let me check if there's a GPU.\n\n\nI should try running a smaller model like qwen2.5:7b instead to see if that works better with the available resources, and also check the Ollama logs to understand what's happening during the load process.\n","thinkingSignature":"c5a464fb1f65c9ec46c42e3c5ebbe30a266a6866ead3395c624d58b5ba35b110"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gyuwxtf2deoy_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ollama ps 2>&1; echo \"---\"; Get-CimInstance Win32_VideoController | Select-Object Name, @{N='VRAM(GB)';E={[math]::Round($_.AdapterRAM/1GB,1)}} 2>&1","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":92,"output":270,"cacheRead":82688,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":83050,"cost":{"input":0.0000276,"output":0.00032399999999999996,"cacheRead":0.004961279999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005312879999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778585387451,"responseId":"0652422c0d5780efcfef2e16526a265d"}}
{"type":"message","id":"30c45251","parentId":"ac72d1d4","timestamp":"2026-05-12T11:29:57.308Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_gyuwxtf2deoy_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"NAME    ID    SIZE    PROCESSOR    CONTEXT    UNTIL \n---\r\n\r\nName                               VRAM(GB)\r\n----                               --------\r\nParsec Virtual Display Adapter            0\r\nSudoMaker Virtual Display Adapter         0\r\nIntel(R) Iris(R) Xe Graphics              2\r\nNVIDIA GeForce RTX 4050 Laptop GPU        4"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":384,"aggregated":"NAME    ID    SIZE    PROCESSOR    CONTEXT    UNTIL \n---\r\n\r\nName                               VRAM(GB)\r\n----                               --------\r\nParsec Virtual Display Adapter            0\r\nSudoMaker Virtual Display Adapter         0\r\nIntel(R) Iris(R) Xe Graphics              2\r\nNVIDIA GeForce RTX 4050 Laptop GPU        4","cwd":"C:\\Users\\USER\\.openclaw\\agents\\ray"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778585397308}}
{"type":"message","id":"711d8d03","parentId":"30c45251","timestamp":"2026-05-12T11:30:19.250Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I see the full picture:\n- No models currently loaded (ollama ps returns empty)\n- Intel Iris Xe: 2GB (used for display)\n- NVIDIA RTX 4050 Laptop: 4GB VRAM\n\nThe problem is clear now: qwen3.5:4b needs ~4GB just to load, and with only 4GB VRAM on the RTX 4050, running the model + doing inference is very tight. The model was loaded during installation (that's why it took so long) but after installation it gets unloaded.\n\nThe model is working fine but needs to be loaded into VRAM first. When it's loaded, it takes the full 3.4GB and there's barely room left for inference, which is why responses are slow/delayed or empty.\n\n\nThe streaming approach might work better here—since the output stays empty in non-streaming mode, I should try requesting the response in chunks instead. Though honestly, qwen3.5:4b is probably the least suitable model for this laptop given the VRAM constraints; even qwen2.5:7b at 4.7GB would struggle. I should give Jo a clear picture of the situation and what the actual options are.\n","thinkingSignature":"a4797fe83a50b84b4ce415f78cd1d4accc720fed8a36bc30e4bd054e05caeb43"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_l7fo2805e1hp_1","name":"update_plan","arguments":{"plan":[{"status":"completed","step":"收集記憶與腳本、建立知識庫"},{"status":"completed","step":"建立 qwen3.5:4b 訓練 Modelfile（ray-v3）"},{"status":"completed","step":"匯出腳本質量和結構化文件"},{"status":"completed","step":"餵給 qwen3.5:4b 做系統整合學習（Ray Knowledge 已寫入 Modelfile）"},{"status":"in_progress","step":"診斷回應問題"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":200,"output":397,"cacheRead":82752,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":83349,"cost":{"input":0.000059999999999999995,"output":0.0004764,"cacheRead":0.00496512,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00550152}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778585397311,"response